MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/2/2005-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 2nd November, 2005
11 Kartik, 1927(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 1st November,
2005 -
Shri Ghulam Nabi Azad relinquished the charge of the office of the
Minister of Parliamentary Affairs and the Minister of Urban
Development ;
i)
ii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of the Minister
of Urban Development; and
Shri Priyaranjan Dasmunsi assumed the additional charge of the
office of the Minister of Parliamentary Affairs.
ii)
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Copy forwarded for information to:-
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
(K.L. Sharma)
Deputy Secretary (Cabinet)
Copy also forwarded for information to :-
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
(K.L. Sharma)
Deputy Secretary (Cabinet)
